Description:
SPECTACULAR TOWN RESIDENCE
Rejuvenated from the absolute top to the bottom this magnificent 3 bedroom double storey townhouse has been finished in beautiful appointments, fresh white tones and chic styling.
Step inside and be amazed by the beautiful timber flooring lining throughout the home with brand new kitchen featuring stainless steel appliances (including dishwasher) with the added bonus of a built in front loading washing machine.
Move through the dining area and lounge area through double sliding doors to huge courtyard with room for entertaining and additional car/boat/trailer storage if required. Move upstairs to find 3 bedrooms with new carpet, built in robes with a walk in robe and full ensuite to master bedroom with central main bathroom also.
With a long list of features, this home must be seen to be believed.
Mirrored robes
Gloss white arcs and doors
Floor to ceiling tiles in bathroom
Walk in robe
Down lights
New carpet
Large private court yard
Single garage
Eurotag appliances
Washing machine (included)
Stone bench tops
Side gate access

Description:
No Fuss Apartment in a Sensational Location
On the corner of the block and in a convenient location while impressing with low maintenance comfort, this two bedroom upper level apartment is a fantastic lifestyle investment.
Enjoying a prominent position in a block of only a five residences, this wonderful starter showcases a comfortable and fully tiled living zone that's light-filled and kept comfortable with split system heating and cooling. The spotless kitchen adjoins and comes equipped with free standing electric stove and plenty of space to prepare meals. The two well-sized bedrooms are carpeted and come with built-in robes and a quality bathroom enjoys a shower over bath, a separate toilet and comes with terrific laundry facilities.
Ideally suited for first homebuyers, downsizers or avid investors, this inviting abode also features screen doors, security window shutters, communal gardens with clothesline, a car space and a storage room.
In a stellar central location it's close to Gerard Street Reserve, buses, EastLink access, South Eastern Private Hospital, Dandenong Hospital, Chisholm Institute, Yarraman Railway and Dandenong Markets & Plaza.

Located in the amazing Mosaic apartment complex, this property will appeal to everyone from the first home buyer to the astute investor with its immaculate presentation & ideal position. Open plan living meets functionality, with:
